                <div class="eyebrow" data-label="Finance">Finance</div>
                <h1 class="lede-text-only__hed"><span class="lede-text-only__highlight">A Hedge Fund Steps Into Nigeria’s $9 Billion Corporate Dispute</span></h1>
                <div class="lede-text-only__dek">
                <span class="lede-text-only__highlight">
                    <p>The decade-long battle centers on a tiny natural gas company.</p>
                </span>
            </div>
        
                <address class="lede-text-only__byline">By <div class="author">Joe Light
        <div class="author__modal">
            
            
            <a class="author__modal-bio" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/authors/AS3ZVtysLfo/joe-light" rel="author">More stories by Joe Light</a>
        </div>
    </div></address>
